title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Dec 30 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Dec 30 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, "The Czar of Talk" from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, sat in for Clay and Buck on New Year's Eve eve, welcoming Bob Unanue, CEO of Goya Foods, who discusses the supply chain, inflation, and the "buycott" that defeated the left's boycott after he dared say a kind word about Trump. Plus, journalist Jordan Schachtel on the FDA failing to actually approve any covid vaccine.
